snippet.title: Amber Heard Flirts With Aquaman 2 Director AGAIN!
snippet.description:
“I don’t think that we’re ever getting to react to, honestly, pure fan pressure. You gotta do what you are feeling is best for the movie. We felt that if it’s James Wan and Jason Momoa, it should be Amber Heard. That’s really what it had been ,” he said
